variables.title: ButtonDrilldown3
variables.variableValue:
CASE 
			WHEN VBAP.ZZDLZ = '0' THEN '0 - Delivery from SC stock'
			WHEN VBAP.ZZDLZ = '1' THEN '1 - Direct delivery'
			WHEN VBAP.ZZDLZ = '2' THEN '2 - Delivery via SC'
			WHEN VBAP.ZZDLZ = '3' THEN '3 - Delivery via LC'
			WHEN VBAP.ZZDLZ = '4' THEN '4 - Direct dispatch from master plant via 3rd party order div.'
			WHEN VBAP.ZZDLZ = '5' THEN '5 - Direct dispatch from master plant with division'
			END

variables.title: ButtonDrilldown3
variables.variableValue: CASE WHEN PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") >= 0 AND PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 100 THEN 'a) 0 - 100€' WHEN PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 100 AND PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 500 THEN 'b) 100 - 500€' WHEN PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 500 AND PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 1000 THEN 'c) 500 - 1.000€' WHEN PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 1000 AND PU_SUM("VBAK","VBAP"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 10000 THEN 'd) 1.000 - 10.000€' ELSE 'e) > 10.000€' END

formula.text: SUM(CASE WHEN MATCH_ACTIVITIES(NODE['Create Quotation'] ) = 1 THEN 1.0 ELSE 0.0 END)/ COUNT_TABLE(VBAP)

axis0.name: #{activity}
axis0.text: CASE WHEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"  IN (<%=Undesired%>) THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" ELSE NULL END

axis2.name: # <%= CASE_ITEM %>s with Undesired Activities
axis2.text:
COUNT(DISTINCT 
 
CASE WHEN PU_COUNT("<%= CASE_TABLE %>","_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>","_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN (<%=Undesired%>)) > 0 
           AND "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"  IN (<%=Undesired%>) 
THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY" ELSE NULL END
 
)

axis2.name: Undesired Activity Rate
axis2.text:
COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN (<%=Undesired%>) THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY" ELSE NULL END)
/
COUNT(DISTINCT "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY")

axis2.name: UAR only manual execution
axis2.text:
COUNT(DISTINCT 
 
CASE WHEN PU_COUNT("<%= CASE_TABLE %>","_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>","_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" IN (<%=Undesired%>)) > 0 
           AND "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>"  IN (<%=Undesired%>)
                  AND  "_CEL_<%=process%>_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" IN (<%=auto_user_type%>)
THEN "_CEL_<%= process %>_ACTIVITIES"."_CASE_KEY" ELSE NULL END
 
)
